<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.10">
<l>cūteṉṟu kaḷavuñ cūtuñcey yātē</l>
<l>vētamuṉvirittāṉ virumpiyakōyil</l>
<l>mātuṟumayilcēr māliruñcōlai</l>
<l>pōtaviḻmalaiyē pukuvatuporuḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without committing theft and gambling, thinking [them] means,</l>
<l>wealth is entering the mountain where buds open,</l>
<l>Māliruñcōlai joined by beautiful peacocks,</l>
<l>the temple that is desired by him who once expounded the Veda.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
